Class DefaultI18NResourceBundle

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.naoghuman.lib.i18n.internal.DefaultI18NResourceBundle

    public final class DefaultI18NResourceBundle
extends Object
implements I18NResourceBundle
    The default implementation from the interface I18NResourceBundle.

    Given attributes in the methods will be checked by DefaultI18NValidator.

      • setBaseBundleName

        public void setBaseBundleName(String baseBundleName)
        Description copied from interface: I18NResourceBundle
        Sets the baseBundleName which will be used to load the associated ResourceBundle.

        Format from the baseBundleName should be:

        • Package name to the bundle, '.' (point) separated.
        • Base name from the bundles.
        Example:
        • Package: com.github.naoghuman.app.i18n.demo
        • Bundles: message_de.properties, message_en.properties
        • Base bundle name: com.github.naoghuman.app.i18n.demo.message
        Specified by:
        setBaseBundleName in interface I18NResourceBundle
        Parameters:
        baseBundleName - the base bundle name.
